Web/SVG/Element/missing-glyph\"><code>&lt;missing-glyph&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/mpath\"><code>&lt;mpath&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>N-P\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Element/path\"><code>&lt;path&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/pattern\"><code>&lt;pattern&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polygon\"><code>&lt;polygon&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/polyline\"><code>&lt;polyline&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>Q-R\n   <ol>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/radialGradient\"><code>&lt;radialGradient&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Element/rect\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;rect&gt;</code></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>S\n   <ol>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/set\"><code>&lt;set&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/stop\"><code>&lt;stop&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/switch\"><code>&lt;switch&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/symbol\"><code>&lt;symbol&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>T\n   <ol>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/text\"><code>&lt;text&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Element/textPath\"><code>&lt;textPath&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li class=\"deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tref\"><code>&lt;tref&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/tspan\"><code>&lt;tspan&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>U\n   <ol>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/use\"><code>&lt;use&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n <li>V-Z\n   <ol>\n     <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Element/view\"><code>&lt;view&gt;</code></a></li>\n     <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/vkern\"><code>&lt;vkern&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n   </ol>\n </li>\n   </ol></details></li>\n   </ol>\n  </section></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\">Das <strong><code>&lt;rect&gt;</code></strong> Element ist ein SVG Element, aus welchem Rechtecke mittels einer definierten Eckposition, einer Höhe und einer Breite erstellt werden können.</span> Zudem sind Rechtecke mit abgerundeten Ecken möglich.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"nutzungskontext","title":"Nutzungskontext","isH3":false,"content":"<p><table class=\"properties\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"row\">Kategorien</th><td>Grundformelement, Grafikelement, Formelement</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Erlaubter Inhalt</th><td>Beliebige Anzahl der folgenden Elemente, in beliebiger Reihenfolge:<br><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Element#animation_elements\">Animationselemente</a><br><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Element#descriptive_elements\">Beschreibende Elemente</a></td></tr></tbody></table></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attribute","title":"Attribute","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"globale_attribute","title":"Globale Attribute","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute#conditional_processing_attributes\">Conditional processing attributes</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute#core_attributes\">Core attributes</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute#graphical_event_attributes\">Graphical event attributes</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute#presentation_attributes\">Presentation attributes</a></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/class\">class</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/style\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">style (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/externalResourcesRequired\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">externalResourcesRequired</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/transform\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">transform (en-US)</a></code></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifische_attribute","title":"Spezifische Attribute","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"x\"><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/x\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">x (en-US)</a></code></dt>\n <dd>Legt die x-Koordinate des rect-Elements fest.</dd>\n <dt id=\"y\"><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/y\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">y (en-US)</a></code></dt>\n <dd>Legt die y-Koordinate des rect-Elements fest.</dd>\n <dt id=\"width\"><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/width\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">width (en-US)</a></code></dt>\n <dd>Legt die Breite des rect-Elements fest.</dd>\n <dt id=\"height\"><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/height\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">height (en-US)</a></code></dt>\n <dd>Legt die Höhe des rect-Elements fest.</dd>\n <dt id=\"rx\"><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/rx\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">rx (en-US)</a></code></dt>\n <dd>Legt den horizontalen Eckradius des rect-Elements fest.</dd>\n <dt id=\"ry\"><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/ry\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">ry (en-US)</a></code></dt>\n <dd>Legt den vertikalen Eckradius des rect-Elements fest.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"dom_interface","title":"DOM Interface","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieses Element implementiert das <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGRectElement\"><code>SVGRectElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Interface.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele"